title: President Obama to be one of David Letterman's final guests
text:
President Obama to be one of David Letterman's final guests By Frank Pallotta @frankpallotta There will be many guests in the final shows of David Letterman's late night career, but the biggest may be the Leader of the Free World. 
President Obama will appear on "The Late Show" on May 4, CBS announced on Friday. 
The appearance will come just weeks before Letterman signs off on May 20. 
This will mark the president's eighth and final visit on the show. CNNMoney (New York) May 1, 2015: 11:22 AM ET
